beer.beer_description:
The Foo Brew is the first beer to be produced by Willie the Boatman Brewery, based in St Peters, NSW.

The Foo brew is a beautiful Golden Ale designed to be a session beer. With three hop additions of Cascade this beer  is a fine balance between the hops and the malt base. PLease drink to enjoy.
